snippet.textDisplay:
The method to kill monkey
Step 1: catch the real sun wukong*
Step 2: stick him in the brazier of eight trigrams.
Step 3: light brazier and keep it blazing at maximum temperature for no less than 147 days.
Step 4: after minimum number of days has been exceededinvoke loophole to get around the bureaucracy of heaven to invoke the three catastrophes all at once so that the brazier and monkey inside of it is incinerated by fire struck by lightning and finally disintegrated to dust.
Step 5: take a whiz on the dust for good measure.

* Do note that if you fail to catch The monkey King 😂 you're hosed.
